title: GREAT 3 BEDROOM APT
posting_body: ['Great apartment located at 2611 Pillsbury Ave South.', 'Situated in a 4 plex this is a DIFFERENT living experience.', 'All apartments are occupied by professional people or grad students, its a safe and stable living environment and you will have the opportunity to speak with other tenants if you desire, I will facilitate that.', 'Nobody moving in and out or other wierd stuff going on... Lowkey and mellow environment.', 'I (the landlord)take care of any repairs either the same day or will get back to you with a repair plan.', "You won't be dealing with some inpersonal managment company.", 'I have long-term tenants because they like the environment', 'and I keep the rent a bit below market to keep good folks.', "It works and I think you'll like the atmosphere and philosophy of the place.", 'There is off street parking, on site laundry, extra lockable storage in the basement.', 'A wooden fenced back yard with patio,gardens and pergala offers the opportunity to grill and relax.', 'You can plant veggies or flowers if you like.', "If you've read this far we may likely be a good fit.", "I'm seeking folks who are responsible...you know who you are.", 'Two bedrooms are on the second floor with new hardwood flooring.', 'First floor has wood floors and ceramic tile in the bath and kitchen.', 'Clean, bright and fresh, ample closet space.', 'PLEASE note the move in date is 31 July', 'Smoking out side only', 'Located at 2609 Pillsbury Ave South, on the fringe of Uptown, one block from EAT STREET and the Art Institute, a great location for the bohemian lifestyle.', "Sorry, I'm a tad computer challenged so I can't post pictures but if the vibe feels right then you should come check the place out.", 'Utilities seperate.', 'Water & garbage is $40 paid with rent.', '$500 security deposit.', 'Cat okay, no dogs, elephants etc.', 'Available JULY 1', 'Call Morris at', 'show contact info', 'for more info or to arrange a showing.']
